userdoc.notice: Gets the exchange rate between the underlying asset and the peg asset by using:          1. weETH Oracle price for weETH -> eETH = ETH (pegged)          2. result from 1. combined with a uniV3CheckCLRSOracle to get someToken (e.g. ETH) -> someToken2.          e.g. when going from weETH to USDC:          1. weETH -> eETH = ETH via weETH Oracle          2. ETH -> USDC via UniV3 ETH <> USDC pool checked against ETH -> USDC Chainlink feed.
